ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course is very important to your academic career. There are a lot of legal issues related to workplace conduct that you need to be familiar with. Unfortunately, a lot of the material on ethical conduct of research will not be applicable to mathematicians, but he will mostly skim these topics. You should take this class.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course was not related to my research topic directly, but it will be very helpful to my research in general and to my relationships with collaborators and colleagues.
